item.title: Download Speed
item.dc:creator: @NewbieNewty Newty
item.description:
@NewbieNewty wrote:

Assuming your getting good wireless signal and your still downloading slow then its probably the torrent. Try downloading a file from a big host like microsoft.com or do a speedtest. If your speed is good there then the problem is definitely the torrent. Try to find one with more seeders.
